{"tid":2334122,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Samsung 悄悄刪除嘲諷 Apple 不附送充電器帖子","createTime":"2020-12-21T03:10:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-22T11:25:18.000Z","uid":1121,"like":19,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"715fa5e1697d6f60c23ec401b4e86f253c1b2e91","tid":2334122,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:10:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Samsung-Charger-696x364.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F12%2FSamsung-Charger-696x364.jpg&h=a90308cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\niPhone 12 系列發佈後，不附送充電器的決定令很多 Android 手機廠「群起」嘲諷，而 Samsung 的嘲諷可算是最多人留意的一個，不過有網民發現該帖文已從 Facebook 悄悄移除。<br />\n<br />\n該帖文在 10 月 iPhone 12 發佈會之後貼出，當時張貼了一幅圖像，圖像中展示的是 Samsung 隨附於手機的電源轉接器，並在圖片底部寫道「Included with your Galaxy」，意思是「包含在你的 Galaxy 產品包裝內」。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，Samsung 向巴西監管機構提供的一些即將推出的 Galaxy 手機資料顯示，Samsung 會跟隨 Apple 不再附機附設充電器及耳機。當中包括 Galaxy S21、S21+ 及 S21 Ultra。現在 Samsung 將該嘲諷 Apple 帖文刪除後，相信未來  Galaxy 手機跟隨 iPhone 不附送充電器的機會大大提升。"},{"pid":"c38f35aa53d6586bbd3c20857fcdf2ccd51b1cd6","tid":2334122,"uid":26535,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"屋企人連自己應該接近10個插頭 不過apple應該比人簡要唔要"},{"pid":"f84c71cde1d4622d5dcc4ed19dd7f23f42451fc0","tid":2334122,"uid":653,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:16:42.000Z","msg":"三叔成日都好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又要抽水自己又跟風"},{"pid":"a22a1e7d6c4a3cca4ce1f040ab77692eb780742f","tid":2334122,"uid":10397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c38f35aa53d6586bbd3c20857fcdf2ccd51b1cd6","tid":2334122,"uid":26535,"like":3,"dislike":9,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"屋企人連自己應該接近10個插頭 不過apple應該比人簡要唔要"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-21T03:17:30.000Z","msg":"蘋果話減咗插頭同包裝錢<br />\n要既你自己另外買"},{"pid":"a24fc58ceb71e04a03008aebedf4ecaeeb53137